        "content": "<p>Hi everyone! I'm playing a bit with the new compiler and I can't figure out how to call math functions. Does the Num module still exists ?</p>",
        "id": 576901776,
        "sender_full_name": "Guillaume Sarisson",
        "timestamp": 1772522207
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>No it doesn't --- src/build/roc/Builtin.roc defines all the builtin functions</p>",
        "id": 576902104,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1772522356
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://github.com/roc-lang/roc/blob/3fa8df31997e3e233d5bda63eec8737ccd3ce941/src/build/roc/Builtin.roc#L4\">https://github.com/roc-lang/roc/blob/3fa8df31997e3e233d5bda63eec8737ccd3ce941/src/build/roc/Builtin.roc#L4</a></p>",
        "id": 576902120,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1772522366
    },
    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>$ roc repl\nRoc REPL\nType :help for help, :exit to quit\n\n» U16.plus(12,32)\n44\n» 12 + 23\n35\n» U32.div_by(12,3)\n4\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 576902341,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1772522470
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Cool, it works. Thanks !</p>",
        "id": 576902828,
        "sender_full_name": "Guillaume Sarisson",
        "timestamp": 1772522658
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It's a bit funky... but you can do </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>» 12.U64.plus(12)\n24\n» 12.plus(12)\n24\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 576902958,
